Package carpark

Demonstration package using monitors to implement a simple car park system.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Arrivals
    Models a stream of cars entering a car park.
    CarPark
    Implements a car park, with a stream of cars entering and leaving.
    CarParkControl
    Controls a car park, and two streams of cars, one modelling cars arriving, and the other cars leaving.
    Departures
    Models a stream of cars leaving a car park.
